sequenceDiagram
autonumber
participant Game
participant UI
participant Scoreboard

Game-->>Game: enter GameOver state (freeze board)
Game->>UI: showLoseMenu()

UI->>Scoreboard: addAttempt()
Scoreboard-->>UI: updated

UI-->>Game: wait for player choice
alt Restart
  UI->>Game: restartLevel()
  Game-->>Game: resetLevel()
else Next (if allowed)
  UI->>Game: nextLevel()
  Game-->>Game: loadNextLevel()
else Exit
  UI->>Game: exitToMenu()
  Game-->>Game: mainMenu()
end